   "source": [
    "2. A bag contains one marble which is either green or blue, with equal probabilities. A green\n",
    "marble is put in the bag (so there are 2 marbles now), and then a random marble is taken\n",
    "out. The marble taken out is green. What is the probability that the remaining marble is also\n",
    "green?"
   ]
